    "It encompasses a range of technical and procedural controls aimed at proactively safeguarding against both internal and external threats.",
    "AI technology can significantly enhance the resilience of systems by facilitating various protective measures.• User authentication-Instead of relying on easily compromised credentials like usernames and passwords, AI can improve authentication through the use of physical biometrics, behavioral biometrics, or multi-factor authentication.",
    "Physical biometrics involves utilizing unique physical characteristics of individuals, such as fingerprints, iris patterns, or bio-signals, for identification."
